g.text: Initiates the process of overviewing the tests
Requests to delimit the period of dates to analyze
Selects the dates and asks to see relative information
Shows successfully the relative information ( number of clients, number of tests Waiting for results,
the number of tests Waiting for diagnosis, total number of tests processed
in the laboratory in each day, week, month and year
Selects the algorithm and asks for the least effective time
Shows successfully the least effective time
